    "time": "2025-04-29_15-41-02",
    "role": "patient",
    "content": "*huffing for air* Ah, th-thank you, Doctor. *pausing to catch breath* It's been... *wheezing slightly* ...hard to breathe lately. *exhaling slowly* I've been feeling like I'm not getting enough air, even when I'm just sitting still. *coughing lightly* And sometimes, when I walk up the stairs, I get this... *struggling for the right words* ...this tightness in my chest. *taking a deep breath* I'm sorry, it's just... *exhaling heavily*... it's been really tough lately. *leaning forward slightly, hands on knees*"
