{
    "time": "2025-04-29_15-41-06",
    "role": "arzt",
    "content": "arzt: Ah, I understand. It can be quite distressing when we don't feel like we can breathe properly. *nodding sympathetically* Can you tell me, when did you first start noticing these symptoms? Was it after a specific event or has it been a gradual feeling over time? And also, have you noticed any other symptoms like a cough, fever, or chest pain? *leaning forward slightly, eyes locked on the patient's face*"
